<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_description">
 <h2>
  About This Game
 </h2>
 A light-hearted game about mischief where you guide a band of fairies with a simple goal.
 <br/>
 <span class="bb_img_ctn">
  <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="160" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302320/extras/a2d0b0e5821e0665b94354cbc1d039ee.poster.avif?t=1774028515" width="436">
   <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302320/extras/a2d0b0e5821e0665b94354cbc1d039ee.webm?t=1774028515" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
   <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302320/extras/a2d0b0e5821e0665b94354cbc1d039ee.mp4?t=1774028515" type="video/mp4"/>
  </video>
 </span>
 <br/>
 <br/>
 However toads don't like being poked and will not sit idle after the offense. Use the unique abilities of each fairy to get the upper hand or even turn the toads attack into your advantage. Protecting the blue fairy is all you need to worry about.
 <br/>
 <br>
  This is a puzzle game that puts its cartoony art as one of the main protagonists. Watch your fairies run around the world, sleep in inappropriate places, react to the environment or get flung into the air.
  <br>
   <br>
    The game features over 100 levels in vibrant worlds, each one introducing new mysterious contraptions and tricky toad varieties. Learn how they work through observation and experimentation.
    <br>
     <span class="bb_img_ctn">
      <img class="bb_img" height="235" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302320/extras/df20d47a0927d789ea7d849610d6997c.avif" width="256"/>
     </span>
     <br/>
     Learning, as well as getting punished by your actions, is part of the fun.
    </br>
   </br>
  </br>
 </br>
