<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_description">
 <h2>
  About This Game
 </h2>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video aria-label="Let's start from scratch..." autoplay="" class="bb_img" crossorigin="anonymous" height="100" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fab6df7767e6384fcaf9dcecd27efa44.poster.avif?t=1773831686" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fab6df7767e6384fcaf9dcecd27efa44.webm?t=1773831686" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <strong>
   Scritchy Scratchy is a super-satisfying scratch card incremental game where luck is your weapon, and glittering riches are just a scratch away.
  </strong>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Dive into a growing collection of scratchers, each with its own quirks, surprises, and sometimes downsides. Rip through tickets, uncover rare symbols, tweak your own luck, and chase absurd payouts.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Unlock Scratch Bot, your tireless mechanical friend who scratches and reveals the rewards for you. Turn your run into a full-blown jackpot engine as your balance shoots through the roof while you sit back and relax.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video aria-label="A series of bouncing scratch cards." autoplay="" class="bb_img" crossorigin="anonymous" height="100" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fdf689d4fafe4ee00eb599a220608ebc.poster.avif?t=1773831686" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fdf689d4fafe4ee00eb599a220608ebc.webm?t=1773831686" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video aria-label="Scratch. Upgrade. Repeat." autoplay="" class="bb_img" crossorigin="anonymous" height="100" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/e4c6c7305f500d246e41db1d3d0c43d2.poster.avif?t=1773831686" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/e4c6c7305f500d246e41db1d3d0c43d2.webm?t=1773831686" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  As you prosper, you’ll unlock upgrades that twist luck in your favor:
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  • Boosted odds and payouts
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  • Faster and easier scratching
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  • New scratch card variants with unique rules
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  But power always comes with risk. Some cards tempt you with monstrous payouts at the cost of nasty penalties. Some offer steady income… others threaten your entire run. Will you play like a sensible adult or gamble like a degenerate in a neon casino?
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video aria-label="Multiple scratch cards being scratched." autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="380" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/3727db2d3c357cc693037794f20d5035.poster.avif?t=1773831686" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/3727db2d3c357cc693037794f20d5035.webm?t=1773831686" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/3727db2d3c357cc693037794f20d5035.mp4?t=1773831686" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video aria-label="To the moon!" autoplay="" class="bb_img" crossorigin="anonymous" height="100" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/432c130a7bc4d83bd29bb6bc0d345058.poster.avif?t=1773831686" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/432c130a7bc4d83bd29bb6bc0d345058.webm?t=1773831686" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  When you’re ready for even more madness, Prestige to reset your run, gather Jack Points, and spend them on permanent upgrades that reshape your strategy. Build your own luck engine: Slow and steady, wildly explosive, or pure chaos.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Scritchy Scratchy is a dangerously satisfying progression casino, where every scratch is a little dopamine hit, and every run is one lucky break away from the big jackpot!
 </p>
