 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Everwind is a novel take on the RPG and Sandbox Survival genre from First-Person-Perspective.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Embark on an adventure with your friends - Build a base on a flying island-ship, gather resources, craft, loot, and fight while you rise above the clouds to uncover the mysteries of this world!
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph" style="text-align: center">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph" style="text-align: center">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <img class="bb_img" height="45" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/46e2d241119f41133bb26f99cc152d30.webp" width="616"/>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph" style="text-align: center">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" crossorigin="anonymous" height="316" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253100/extras/3cfd011d15d44f889d88813e0c07b900.poster.avif?t=1773865886" width="616">
